data.description: Enjoy putting your personal touch in this Ocean Pointe 5 Bedroom 3 ½ Bath Single Family Home. Free-flow and continuity between living spaces. 4 bedrooms (all upstairs) 2 ½ baths in main house. 5th bedroom (approx. 200 sq ft) w/full bath is a separate room (studio) attached to the 2-car enclosed garage with its own entrance. It is perfect for extended family, guests or your home office.  Located in a sought-after community with a short drive to wonderful amenities.
